# Local dev secrets for `wrangler dev`. Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored).
# For production, set these with `wrangler secret put <NAME>`.

# 0x-prefixed private key of the hot wallet whose address has
# setApprovalForAll(true) on the parent name's NameWrapper position. Gas is
# paid by Pimlico via the paymaster-proxy, so this wallet does NOT need an
# ETH balance — but its derived address MUST appear in the proxy's
# OPERATOR_ALLOWLIST_1 secret or the policy will reject the UserOp. Treat
# as a hot key — revoke NameWrapper approval from the owner wallet if it leaks.
MAINNET_OPERATOR_KEY=

# Comma-separated CORS allowlist (optional; defaults to *).
ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000

# All RPC traffic (Sepolia membership check + mainnet NameWrapper reads +
# sponsored mint UserOps) routes through the deployed paymaster-proxy via
# @ipe-gov/sdk's `paymasterProxyRpcUrl` helper — no RPC URLs needed here.
